## Ingredients
½ cup unsweetened almond milk
2 tablespoons chia seeds
½ teaspoon maple syrup or honey 
⅛ teaspoon cinnamon

## Optional toppings
Chopped nuts and raisins
Coconut flakes

## Instructions
In a lidded jar, combine the almond milk, chia seeds, maple syrup or honey,and cinnamon. 
Stir it to combine. Keep it aside for two hours, then give it a good stir 
Serve with toppings like Chopped nuts, raisins, coconut flakes. You can add blueberries or
strawberries depends on your taste.

